<item>
            <title>[OAK-427] ItemDelegate has dependency to TreeImpl#NullLocation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-427</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The item-delegate has a dependency to NullLocation which is a&lt;br/&gt;
inner class of TreeImpl and as such is an implementation detail.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12614990">OAK-427</key>
            <summary>ItemDelegate has dependency to TreeImpl#NullLocation</summary>
